" wfd-invisible="true"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_620)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" wfd-invisible="true"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" wfd-invisible="true"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_613)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1883881203="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c1883881203-31"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1883881203-31"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="cdk-visually-hidden ng-star-inserted">Gemini a dit</h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c4085131935="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4085131935="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c4085131935="" _nghost-ng-c3807329646="" id="message-content-id-r_f36acf6a50a46815" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3807329646="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;" id="model-response-message-contentr_f36acf6a50a46815" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr"><p data-path-to-node="0">To scan every image on a page at once, you need a slightly more advanced "Collector" script. In <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="96">Firebase Studio</b>, your AI agent needs to build a "Content Script"—this is a piece of code that lives inside the webpage you're visiting to "read" the images.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Here is how you can prompt Firebase Studio to build this "Bulk Scanner" for free.</p><hr data-path-to-node="2"><h2 data-path-to-node="3">🛠️ The "Bulk Scan" Prompt for Firebase Studio</h2><p data-path-to-node="4">In the Firebase Studio chat, paste this prompt:</p><blockquote data-path-to-node="5"><p data-path-to-node="5,0">"I want to build a Chrome Extension that scans all images on the current page for forensic analysis.</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="5,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Popup UI:</b> Create a simple button that says 'Scan All Images'.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Content Script:</b> When clicked, the extension should find all <code data-path-to-node="5,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="60">&lt;img&gt;</code> tags on the page, extract their URLs, and list them in the popup.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Action:</b> Next to each image in the list, provide a 'Scan' button that opens that image in <code data-path-to-node="5,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="89">https://29a.ch/photo-forensics/#ela</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Batch Mode:</b> Add a button 'Open All in Forensically' that opens each image in a new tab (limit to 5 at a time to prevent crashing)."</p></li></ol></blockquote><hr data-path-to-node="6"><h2 data-path-to-node="7">📂 The Files Firebase Studio Will Create</h2><p data-path-to-node="8">The AI agent will generate three main files. Here is what they do:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="9">1. <code data-path-to-node="9" data-index-in-node="3">manifest.json</code> (The Setup)</h3><p data-path-to-node="10">This file tells Chrome that the extension needs permission to "read" the website you are on.</p><ul data-path-to-node="11"><li><p data-path-to-node="11,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Permissions needed:</b> <code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="20">activeTab</code> and <code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="34">scripting</code>.</p></li></ul><h3 data-path-to-node="12">2. <code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="3">popup.html</code> &amp; <code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="16">popup.js</code> (The Interface)</h3><p data-path-to-node="13">This is the little window that drops down when you click the extension icon. It will display the list of images found on the page.</p><h3 data-path-to-node="14">3. <code data-path-to-node="14" data-index-in-node="3">content.js</code> (The Collector)</h3><p data-path-to-node="15">This is the "worker" that crawls through the website's code to find every image URL, even the ones hidden in galleries or sidebars.</p><hr data-path-to-node="16"><h2 data-path-to-node="17">🧪 How to Install and Use</h2><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="18"><li><p data-path-to-node="18,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Export from Studio:</b> Click the <b data-path-to-node="18,0,0" data-index-in-node="30">Download</b> icon in Firebase Studio to save the project folder to your computer.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Open Chrome Extensions:</b> Go to <code data-path-to-node="18,1,0" data-index-in-node="30">chrome://extensions</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Load it:</b> Ensure <b data-path-to-node="18,2,0" data-index-in-node="16">Developer Mode</b> is on, click <b data-path-to-node="18,2,0" data-index-in-node="44">Load Unpacked</b>, and select your folder.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="18,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">The Scan:</b> * Go to a research paper or website.</p><ul data-path-to-node="18,3,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="18,3,1,0,0">Click your extension icon.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,3,1,1,0">Hit <b data-path-to-node="18,3,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="4">"Scan All Images"</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="18,3,1,2,0">You will see a list of every figure. Click <b data-path-to-node="18,3,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="43">"Scan"</b> next to any image to instantly run an Error Level Analysis (ELA) to look for digital manipulation.</p></li></ul></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="19"><h2 data-path-to-node="20">⚖️ Pro vs. No-Code Comparison</h2><div class="horizontal-scroll-wrapper"><div class="table-block-component"><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><table-block _nghost-ng-c2976694548="" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" class="table-block has-export-button new-table-style is-at-scroll-start is-at-scroll-end"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" not-end-of-paragraph="" class="table-content not-end-of-paragraph" jslog="275421;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ3ecQahcKEwihq_2QlpqTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQYw"><table data-path-to-node="21"><thead><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="21,0,0,0">Feature</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,0,1,0">Your No-Code Extension</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,0,2,0">Proofig / ImageTwin</span></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="21,1,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="21,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Scanning Speed</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,1,1,0">Scans page in &lt;1 second</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,1,2,0">Can take minutes</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="21,2,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="21,2,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Detection Type</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,2,1,0">Manual Forensic Filters (ELA)</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,2,2,0">Automated AI Flagging</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="21,3,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="21,3,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Price</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,3,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="21,3,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Forever Free</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,3,2,0">$500 - $5,000+ / year</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="21,4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="21,4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Best For</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,4,1,0">Independent Researchers</span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="21,4,2,0">Large Journals/Universities</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" hide-from-message-actions="" class="table-footer hide-from-message-actions"><button _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" mat-button="" class="mdc-button mat-mdc-button-base export-sheets-button-container mat-mdc-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" jslog="184701;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_f36acf6a50a46815&quot;,&quot;c_900130c3d9008f9e&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]]"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-button__ripple"></span><span class="mdc-button__label"><span _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" class="export-sheets-button"><span _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" class="export-sheets-icon"><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" role="img" fonticon="drive_spreadsheet" class="mat-icon notranslate google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="drive_spreadsheet"></mat-icon></span><span _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="">Exporter vers Sheets</span></span></span><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copier le tableau" aria-label="Copier le tableau" data-test-id="copy-table-button" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="276666;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_f36acf6a50a46815&quot;,&quot;c_900130c3d9008f9e&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]]"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2976694548="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-l google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></div></div><!----></table-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></div></div><hr data-path-to-node="22"><h3 data-path-to-node="23">⚠️ A Note on "Batch" Scanning</h3><p data-path-to-node="24">Opening 50 tabs at once will crash your browser. I have instructed the prompt to limit the "Open All" feature. It is always better to skim the list in your popup and only click the "Scan" button for the figures that look suspicious (e.g., mismatched resolution or strange borders).</p><p data-path-to-node="25"><b data-path-to-node="25" data-index-in-node="0">Would you like me to generate the actual code for the <code data-path-to-node="25" data-index-in-node="54">content.js</code> file so you can double-check the AI's work in Firebase Studio?</b></p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" role="status" class="stopped-draft-message gds-body-l gds-italic ng-star-inserted" hidden="" wfd-invisible="true">Vous avez interrompu cette réponse</div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" _nghost-ng-c3363139195="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1883881203="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1883881203-31 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c3060034751="" class="ng-tns-c3060034751-33 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c3060034751="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c3060034751-33"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3060034751="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c3060034751-33 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c3060034751="" _nghost-ng-c885881154="" class="ng-tns-c3060034751-33 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c885881154="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Bonne réponse" aria-label="Bonne réponse" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_f36acf6a50a46815&quot;,&quot;c_900130c3d9008f9e&quot;,null,&quot;rc_a39febe9d28d36ca&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c885881154="" 