p="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" wfd-invisible="true"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_1388)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" wfd-invisible="true"><g><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g><g style="display: none;" wfd-invisible="true"><g><path stroke="url(#__lottie_element_1381)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="miter" fill-opacity="0" stroke-miterlimit="4"></path></g></g></g></svg></div></div></bard-avatar><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1883881203="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c1883881203-61"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="response-content ng-tns-c1883881203-61"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="thoughts-container ng-star-inserted"><!----></div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="cdk-visually-hidden ng-star-inserted">Gemini a dit</h2><!----><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c4085131935="" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4085131935="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c4085131935="" _nghost-ng-c3807329646="" id="message-content-id-r_c73dfb5b3c3c3ee2" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3807329646="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: linear;" id="model-response-message-contentr_c73dfb5b3c3c3ee2" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false" dir="ltr"><p data-path-to-node="0">This error happens because the <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="31">manifest.json</code> file is looking for image files (your extension icons) that don't actually exist in the folder yet. When you build an extension in <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="176">Firebase Studio</b>, the AI often writes the <i data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="217">code</i> for the icons but doesn't always generate the actual <code data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="275">.png</code> files.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Here is how to fix this in 3 minutes:</p><hr data-path-to-node="2"><h3 data-path-to-node="3">1. The "Quick Fix" (Delete the Requirement)</h3><p data-path-to-node="4">If you don't care about having a custom icon right now and just want the extension to work:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="5"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,0,0">Open the <code data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="9">manifest.json</code> file in a text editor (Notepad, VS Code, or back in Firebase Studio).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,0">Look for the <code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="13">"action"</code> or <code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="25">"icons"</code> section. It probably looks like this:</p><response-element class="" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c1595775995="" class="ng-tns-c1595775995-69 ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="code-block ng-tns-c1595775995-69 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c73dfb5b3c3c3ee2&quot;,&quot;c_900130c3d9008f9e&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c993e75e1252c826&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwihq_2QlpqTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ9gE"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-title-s ng-tns-c1595775995-69 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="ng-tns-c1595775995-69">JSON</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="buttons ng-tns-c1595775995-69 ng-star-inserted"><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" aria-label="Copier le code" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Copier le code" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c1595775995-69 mat-unthemed ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c73dfb5b3c3c3ee2&quot;,&quot;c_900130c3d9008f9e&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c993e75e1252c826&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" role="img" fonticon="content_copy" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-s google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="content_copy"></mat-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c1595775995-69"><div _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c1595775995-69"><pre _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" class="ng-tns-c1595775995-69"><code _ngcontent-ng-c1595775995="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c1595775995-69"><span class="hljs-string">"action"</span>: {
  <span class="hljs-attr">"default_icon"</span>: {
    <span class="hljs-attr">"16"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"icon16.png"</span>,
    <span class="hljs-attr">"48"</span>: <span class="hljs-string">"icon48.png"</span>,
