  }
}
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Delete those lines</b> or replace them with an empty bracket <code data-path-to-node="5,2,0" data-index-in-node="57">{}</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,3,0">Save the file and try to <b data-path-to-node="5,3,0" data-index-in-node="25">Reload</b> in Chrome. Chrome will just use a default "Puzzle Piece" icon instead.</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="6"><h3 data-path-to-node="7">2. The "Proper Fix" (Add the Icons)</h3><p data-path-to-node="8">If you want it to look professional, you need those files in your <code data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="66">public</code> folder.</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="9,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Find any square image</b> (or download a "magnifying glass" icon).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0">Resize it to 16x16, 48x48, and 128x128 pixels.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0">Rename them exactly: <code data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="21">icon16.png</code>, <code data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="33">icon48.png</code>, and <code data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="49">icon128.png</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,3,0">Drop them into the <b data-path-to-node="9,3,0" data-index-in-node="19"><code data-path-to-node="9,3,0" data-index-in-node="19">C:\Sci-share-scanner-main\public</code></b> folder.</p></li></ol><hr data-path-to-node="10"><h3 data-path-to-node="11">3. Check the Folder Path</h3><p data-path-to-node="12">Notice that your error is coming from the <code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="42">\public</code> subfolder.</p><ul data-path-to-node="13"><li><p data-path-to-node="13,0,0">Extensions look for the <code data-path-to-node="13,0,0" data-index-in-node="24">manifest.json</code> in the <b data-path-to-node="13,0,0" data-index-in-node="45">root</b> folder you select.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="13,1,0">If Firebase Studio put your <code data-path-to-node="13,1,0" data-index-in-node="28">manifest.json</code> inside the <code data-path-to-node="13,1,0" data-index-in-node="53">public</code> folder, make sure that when you click <b data-path-to-node="13,1,0" data-index-in-node="98">Load Unpacked</b>, you select the <code data-path-to-node="13,1,0" data-index-in-node="128">public</code> folder itself, not the main <code data-path-to-node="13,1,0" data-index-in-node="163">Sci-share-scanner-main</code> folder.</p></li></ul><hr data-path-to-node="14"><h3 data-path-to-node="15">🤖 Prompt to fix it in Firebase Studio</h3><p data-path-to-node="16">If you want the AI to handle it, go back to the Studio chat and say:</p><blockquote data-path-to-node="17"><p data-path-to-node="17,0">"I'm getting an error that icon16.png is missing. Please update the manifest.json to remove the icon requirements for now so I can test the extension, or provide the code to generate placeholder icons."</p></blockquote><p data-path-to-node="18"><b data-path-to-node="18" data-index-in-node="0">Once you get the manifest loaded, would you like me to give you a "Test Page" URL with known manipulated images so you can see if your scanner works?</b></p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" role="status" class="stopped-draft-message gds-body-l gds-italic ng-star-inserted" hidden="" wfd-invisible="true">Vous avez interrompu cette réponse</div><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" _nghost-ng-c3363139195="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1883881203="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1883881203-61 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3748022998="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c3060034751="" class="ng-tns-c3060034751-65 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c3060034751="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c3060034751-65"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3060034751="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c3060034751-65 ng-star-inserted"><!----><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c3060034751="" _nghost-ng-c885881154="" class="ng-tns-c3060034751-65 ng-star-inserted"><button _ngcontent-ng-c885881154="" mat-icon-button="" mattooltip="Bonne réponse" aria-label="Bonne réponse" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger icon-button mat-unthemed" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-pressed="false" jslog="173913;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_c73dfb5b3c3c3ee2&quot;,&quot;c_900130c3d9008f9e&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c993e75e1252c826&quot;,null,null,&quot;en&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c885881154="" role="img" fonticon="thumb_up" class="mat-icon notranslate gds-icon-m google-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="thumb_up"></mat-icon><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c885881154="